!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv": "Content-Type"}
    %title Fleamarket_sample_kagawa-e
    = csrf_meta_tags
    = csp_meta_tag
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload'
    -# = javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload'

  %body
    = render "shared/header"
    %div.classA
      %Section.a
        %div.a-a
          %h2.title-contents 人生を変えるフリマアプリ
          %p.a-b  FURIMAは誰でもかんたんに出品・購入ができる
          %p.a-c  フリマアプリです
          .store-btn-top
            = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png", class:"apple-btn"), "#"
            = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png", class:"google-btn"), "#"
          %div.a-d
      %Section.serect__reason__contents
        .reason__intro
          .reason__intro--subtitle
            FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
            .subtitle__after 
          %ul.reasonList
            %li.reason__list
              .reason__list--left__pict
                %span.number
                  %p 1
                = image_tag"/assets/pict-reason-01.jpg",width:300,height:'300'
              %h3.reason__list--left__text
                %span 3分
                ですぐに出品
              %p.reason__list--left__description
                スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
            %li.reason__list
              .reason__list--center__pict
                %span.number
                  %p 2
                = image_tag "/assets/pict-reason-02.jpg",width:300,height:'300'
              %h3.reason__list--center__text
                %span シンプル
                で使いやすい
              %p.reason__list--center__description
                めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
            %li.reason__list
              .reason__list--right__pict
                %span.number
                  %p 3
                = image_tag "/assets/pict-reason-03.jpg",width:300,height:'300'
              %h3.reason__list--right__text
                手数料
                %span 業界最安
              %p.reason__list--right__description
                最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！
      %section.Top__middle
        %div.Top__middle__dl
          %h2.Toptitle-contents 会員数日本一位
          %p.Toptitlle-explan  FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
          %p.Toptitlle-explan  出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
          %p.Toptitlle-explan  欲しかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません
          .store-btn-top
            = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png", class:"apple-btn"), "#"
            = link_to image_tag("/assets/google-play-badge.png", class:"google-btn"), "#"
      %Section.c
      %Section.d
      %Section.e
      %Section.f
    %div.classB
    = render "shared/footer"
    %div.purchase-btn
      %span.purchase-btn-text 出品する
      = link_to (image_tag '/assets/icon_camera.png' , size: '185x50' ,class: "purchase-btn-icon")

